<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft aus dem Achtbuch wegen Kunz Halbreiter, den Heinz Spörl wegen des Tods seines Vaters in Cham in Gefangenschaft gebracht hat, und um Übersendung einer Abschrift an die Stadt Cham.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_298" id="148v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_298_r1l20">Stat cʒu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l21"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde vns hat
                        furgelegt / Heincʒ Spörell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l22">daʒ er <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> genant Cuncʒ
                        halpreiter cʒu kamme in venknüſʒe hab bracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l23">des Jm vor cʒeiten ſeinen vater vom leben cʒum tode
                        braht hab / vnd maint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l24">daʒ derſelber Halpreiter in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> echtpuch ſteen ſüllet <del rend="strikethrough"> vnd hat vns </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">gepeten . daʒ vvir ew darumb ſchrei </del> /
                                <expan>R<ex>ogamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr durch
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l26">den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ Halpreyter in
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> echtpuch <del rend="strikethrough">alſo
                        </del> ſüchen wollet laſʒen . / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l27">vnd wer <del rend="strikethrough">eʒ dann </del> daʒ
                        Jr Jn alſo darynnen fündt daʒ Jr Jm dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l28">des ein ſchrift / . vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        fürderbrief an die Stat cʒu Kamme </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l29"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet . / daʒ wollen
                        etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan>
<expan>Marg<ex>a</ex>r<ex>ete</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_298" id="148v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Stat czu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde, uns hat furgelegt Heincz Spörell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz er
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> genant Cuncz Halpreiter czu Kamme in
                        venknüsze hab bracht, des im vor czeiten seinen vater vom leben czum tode
                        braht hab, und maint, daz derselber Halpreiter in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> echtpuch steen süllet.
                                <expan>R<ex>ogamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Halpreyter in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> echtpuch süchen wollet laszen. Und wer, daz
                        ir in also darynnen fündt, daz ir im dann des ein schrift und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fürderbrief an die stat czu Kamme
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet. Daz wollen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Marg<ex>a</ex>r<ex>ete</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
